{
  "stem": "1938.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Couldn't you do this in the night, to, to run away from me?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He, he couldn't digest that, that I was so fresh, so, so impossible, bad.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I, I said my prayer, and I wait till he shoot me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have nothing to lose.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he, he said, all of a sudden, to, to run after the march.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the other people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was because my father was-- he did so much good, I-- I-- I survive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I believe in this, that my father's--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you believe in it, it's a wonderful thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So anyway, I, I run after this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for being so excited, I had a little pillow or something in my hand that was my belonging.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I dropped it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after maybe 10 minutes, I see him coming to, to the end of this march.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was the last one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And approaching me-- I said, now he's going to shoot me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He gave me this pillow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is such a miracle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can never forget this, as long as I live.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He shot, in my eyes, a lot of girls with his little golden gun.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he didn't shoot me when he caught me running away, escaping.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How did you do exist with food on the march?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is the question which I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes we found an old bone or a old piece of beets on the way when we marched.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We put it here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we lick and lick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from the snow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But one time we had a party.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We went in--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went in, in a, in a, in a stable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the French people were there before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had baked potatoes, whatever, cooked potatoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
